SELECT   c/context/other_context[at0001]/items[at0002]/value/value AS report_id as ,
  c/uid/value AS composition_uid_value as ,
  d/items[at0015]/value/value AS Collection_date_time as ,
  i/items[at0002]/value/id AS lab_system_identifier as ,
  j/protocol[at0004]/items[at0094]/items[at0062]/value/value AS Requester_order_identifier as ,
  j/protocol[at0004]/items[at0094]/items[at0063]/value/value AS Receiver_order_identifier as ,
  n/items[at0001]/value AS Analyte_result as 
        FROM EHR e CONTAINS COMPOSITION c
            CONTAINS (ACTION d[openEHR-EHR-CLUSTER.specimen.v1] and
    ACTION i[openEHR-EHR-CLUSTER.system.v0] and
    ACTION n[openEHR-EHR-CLUSTER.laboratory_test_analyte.v1])
 ORDER BY c /context/start_time/ value DESC
        LIMIT 1
